nodes.text: This droid was an aspiring actress who went to talent school to achieve this. She was a girlfriend of F-29-PSKx, who called her multiple times from a Star*Link booth from the Star Tours spaceport while traveling.
The background for this droid comes from a "Spot the Droid" poster displayed at the Tokyo Disneyland Star Tours, which was translated at the EndorExpress.net fan site.
The droid was likely to have been a 'drag' redress of F-29, shot before the ride opened.
